1601784000.title: CNN Newsroom
1601784000.descr: CNN Newroom provides the most up to date news as it breaks and is the longest running show on the channel, airing twice a day Monday to Friday and throughout the day over the weekends. CNN was founding in 1980 by American media proprietor Ted Turner as a 24 hour cable news channel and has since won multiple media awards.

1601812800.title: Inside Politics
1601812800.descr: Inside Politics is a political talk show, broadcast on CNN and anchored by CNN Chief National Correspondent John King. It features the most important political stories presented by a panel of well-sourced reporters. John King is an experienced reporter who covers the White House, Congress and the campaign trail, and interviews presidents, politicians and voters.

1601816400.title: U.S. State of the Union Address
1601816400.descr: Jake Tapper brings together major news makers, analysts and experts to tackle pressing domestic issues and diplomacy on the global stage.

1601820000.title: Fareed Zakaria GPS
1601820000.descr: Fareed Zakaria GPS is a weekly public affairs show hosted by an American journalist, political scientist, and author Fareed Zakaria. The "GPS" in the show's title stands for "Global Public Square," a reference to the show's focus on international issues and foreign affairs.

1601823600.title: Reliable Sources
1601823600.descr: Reliable Sources is a CNN Sunday morning talk show focused on analysis of the American news media, hosted by Brian Stelter. The media world is thoroughly examined and the news stories of the previous week are covered. The talk show highlights news about news and tells story behind the story, and features one-on-one interviews with journalists taking part in a news event.

1601829000.title: Inside Africa
1601829000.descr: Each week, Inside Africa documentary series on CNN highlights the unique diversity of mysterious Africa, its numerous cultures and religions, peoples, art, music, cuisine, travel and literature, its one-of-a-kind flora and fauna. 1601865000.descr: Marketplace Africa on CNN offers unique access to the latest African market information, with a look at events and developments that impact its business world. Eleni Giokos is the show's host. Every week she interviews figures of business and industry to reveal the economic trends in various regions of Africa and to present the continent's key sectors and corporations.
